{"id": 998, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都享受过哪些春风拂面的服务？", "description": "人生：在十里寒风里夹杂着几缕春风。（题图来自：Zara Picken）", "record_count": 3526, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152336IG54rJAlPc3bFXyg.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-19T12:55:39Z", "options": [{"id": 79872, "content": "早上出门到小区门口，总有开黑车的想拉我！", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182850idNWvUQ0o76lxrcO.jpg", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613587}, {"id": 79878, "content": "新疆不包邮，并自掏邮费，呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601471}, {"id": 79883, "content": "个人觉得以上的回答者多数是美女", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546062}, {"id": 79889, "content": "下雨滴滴打车下车后司机师傅送了一把伞给我", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614600}, {"id": 79890, "content": "为何你们的这些春风拂面的情况我都没遇到过", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538207}, {"id": 79897, "content": "剪头发 洗头 免费按摩20分钟\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572567}, {"id": 79898, "content": "一次从机场出来坐快车，司机师傅一路一直给大家德芙巧克力、牛奶、士力棒。觉得很幸福，因为大晚上坐飞机本来很累。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 587650}, {"id": 80154, "content": "挂上VPN，使用Google服务那一刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527389}, {"id": 79899, "content": "打的回家， 司机师傅说女孩子一个人想闯一片天不容易（精神安慰）", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614357}, {"id": 79902, "content": "生日那天坐飞机办理登机的时候说可以帮我升舱，然而我拒绝了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609279}, {"id": 79903, "content": "抬眼看你的时候碰巧你也在看着我笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601671}, {"id": 79904, "content": "去香港买鞋的时候，帅帅的店员双手递过包装得精致的鞋子，微笑着说：新年快乐！", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614795}, {"id": 79905, "content": "我没有，不过我帮男友带套套", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454285}, {"id": 79909, "content": "朋友送饭到床边", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600361}, {"id": 79911, "content": "没关系，免费住一晚！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599084}, {"id": 80169, "content": "我只不过?事事键盘好不好使而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615968}, {"id": 83241, "content": "叫家长^_^?????", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627805}, {"id": 79916, "content": "客服态度特好 东西到了跟我说不着急付款 您吃完了给客服就行", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337845}, {"id": 79917, "content": "苹果店网上简单预约后，到店快速交钱、取货", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492266}, {"id": 81453, "content": "屈臣氏的导购不理我", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612033}, {"id": 79918, "content": "一份考卷，“没关系，我帮你答”", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611922}, {"id": 79919, "content": "去东莞算不算？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112082}, {"id": 79920, "content": "出租司机说，我免费送你过去～雨太大", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 540127}, {"id": 79922, "content": "主动问我需要什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240236}, {"id": 79923, "content": "修软水机时，师傅帮忙擦地和搬东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614980}, {"id": 82483, "content": "非书设计，其实是平面设计啦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624599}, {"id": 79924, "content": "711把1毛零钱抹掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 79925, "content": "刚好在等你，你从后面过来温柔地摸了一下我的头。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 604126}, {"id": 79926, "content": "升舱", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 102695}, {"id": 80182, "content": "淘宝卖东西有部分质量问题，老板为免着退货麻烦，让我直接摔碎产品直接退钱了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287272}, {"id": 79927, "content": "扣背", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615003}, {"id": 79928, "content": "Domino's从下单到拿到外卖，20分钟，网上还有每一步的流程，什么时候做饼什么时候加馅儿～准得不得了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572208}, {"id": 79929, "content": "1.坐出租车?没零钱 师傅说不用给了   2.自己从网上买好了手机膜去贴  店主说不用不收钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 378085}, {"id": 79931, "content": "作为男的，谁吊过我们", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272649}, {"id": 79934, "content": "滴滴顺风车，司机不收钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458547}, {"id": 80192, "content": "叫外卖用二十多个硬币付钱， 和外卖小哥一手交币一手交粮。外卖小哥抓硬币拽口袋里数都没数就走了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 616078}, {"id": 79939, "content": "年假回家，每天早上醒来都有妈妈做好的饭。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601544}, {"id": 79943, "content": "今天去打印资料，1张A4纸。收费一块。我只有一百的，老板找不开说你有再说吧。其实我只是路过她也不认识我。最后我还是在回来的路上买了瓶水，换了零钱又给了她，哈哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612294}, {"id": 79945, "content": "夜晚路过卖面包?的店 挑选中，老板说行了姑娘大晚上不能这么吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615042}, {"id": 79950, "content": "带着伞具去衣店买衣服，店员帮把伞放到特定的地方，买完以后，店员帮拿伞并把我送到门外。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 613432}, {"id": 79952, "content": "买水果，直接递给我一根香蕉，找钱的拿钱的时候都双手", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 576673}, {"id": 79956, "content": "送快递，送外卖的是个帅哥！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254456}, {"id": 79960, "content": "买的首饰氧化了，两个多月后拿回店里清洗，处理效果不佳但服务员果断给我换了新的，发票都没有要", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615114}, {"id": 79962, "content": "试衣服的时候女服务员帮我穿衣", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 377521}, {"id": 79964, "content": "有點感冒的時候去打個火鍋，服務員非常關心的奉上姜可樂一碗；別問我哪家店，我去海底撈", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 226630}, {"id": 79965, "content": "进店没人跟着我问东问西", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615142}, {"id": 79966, "content": "海底捞", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 604196}, {"id": 80991, "content": "头发做营养 顺便做了手部按摩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618767}, {"id": 79968, "content": "国税局的春风服务，每个公司发本春风宣传手册，副所长还亲自下到企业来关怀，吓死宝宝了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615146}, {"id": 79970, "content": "test", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521521}]}